## 📅 Content Bundle 생성 규칙 (Hugo 표준)

### 날짜 기반 폴더 구조
```
content/post/{연도}/{연도-월-일}-{영어원제-소문자}-season-{시즌번호}-{핵심키워드}/
```

예시: `content/post/2025/2025-01-27-breaking-bad-season-5-redemption-sacrifice/`

### PowerShell 자동 생성 스크립트
```powershell
# Complete script for creating a new content bundle
$today = Get-Date -Format "yyyy-MM-dd"
$year = Get-Date -Format "yyyy"
$title = "your-seo-optimized-title-here"
$folderName = "$today-$title"

# Create directory structure
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path "content/post/$year/$folderName" -Force

# Create index.md with proper front matter
$frontMatter = @"
---
title: "[Category] Human-Readable Title - Subtitle"
description: "SEO-optimized description (150-160 characters)"
date: $today
lastmod: $today
categories: 
- "Primary Category"
- "Secondary Category"
tags: 
- "primary-keyword"
- "secondary-keyword"
- "long-tail-keyword"
image: "featured-image.jpg"
---

Your content here...
"@

$frontMatter | Out-File -FilePath "content/post/$year/$folderName/index.md" -Encoding UTF8
```

